About LA Gurans

Uniting Talent, Spirit, and Victory

Welcome to LA Gurans! Our team is driven by passion, teamwork, and a commitment to excellence on and off the field. LA Gurans is a group of soccer enthusiasts with the goal of having active social involvement in Los Angeles while being one of the most competitive Nepalese soccer teams in the US.

Our Journey

Since our founding, LA Gurans has grown from a local favorite to a formidable force, competing with the best and delivering memorable performances. Our fans are our heartbeat, and together, weâ€™ve set records and reached milestones.
